# SplitMint Implementation & Learning Plan

This document outlines the step-by-step strategy for building SplitMint. We will use a decoupled architecture, which is widely adopted in the industry and excellent for learning.
- **Frontend**: React.js with TypeScript (using Vite for fast builds) and TailwindCSS for styling.
- **Backend**: Python with FastAPI (high performance, great for building REST APIs quickly).
- **Database**: MongoDB (NoSQL document database, free tier on MongoDB Atlas).

